        <Parent_String>alluvial fans [300008759], fluvial landforms [300132328], landforms (terrestrial) [300266060], natural landscapes [300132294], landscapes (environments) [300008626], Settlements and Landscapes (hierarchy name) [300008346], Built Environment (hierarchy name) [300264550], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
